dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents traffic volumes for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2000. The dataset was originally published by the Madison Area Transportation Planning Board in 2000.[This layer is a detailed line coverage of the Dane County roadway network. The line work was developed as part of the Fly Dane 1995 orthophotography project. This data set has been joined with the master street name file and published in shapefile format; attributes from both datasets are described below.]
